config QCOM_BALANCE_ANON_FILE_RECLAIM
	bool "During reclaim treat anon and file backed pages equally"
	depends on SWAP
	help
	  When performing memory reclaim treat anonymous and file backed pages
	  equally.
	  Swapping anonymous pages out to memory can be efficient enough to justify
	  treating anonymous and file backed pages equally.
config MSM_HELIOSCOM
        tristate "Provide APIs to communicate with Helios chipset"
        help
                HELIOSCOM is a thin layer above SPI. It is used whithin a SoC for
                communication between G-Link/helios_com_dev and Helios processor over SPI.
                This handle the interrupts raised by BG and notify the G-link with
                interrupt event and event data.
config MSM_HELIOSCOM_INTERFACE
        tristate "Driver support for Slate Communication"
        depends on MSM_HELIOSCOM
        help
                Create a helios_com_dev device node for user space communication.
                Single user space client can open device node for communication
                from hardware. Hardware will provide access to read
                registers and read/write AHB memory in the device.

config QTI_OEMVM_CORE_CTL
	tristate "OEMVM CPU control scheme for Hypervisor"
	depends on GUNYAH_DRIVERS
	help
	  This driver provides simple core control features for OEMVM. The vCPU
	  mapping information is recorded when OEMVM bootup. The driver provides
	  API for user to migrate vCPU to current pCPU then yield on current
	  pCPU. User can also recover vCPU mapping after work is done.

